  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> [Insert Date]</p>

  <p>Thank you for using our app ("we", "our", or "us"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile application (the "App").</p>

  <p>By using the App, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree, please do not use the App.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

  <h3>a. Mobile Number</h3>
  <p>We collect your mobile phone number during registration or login. This is used to facilitate communication (e.g., via WhatsApp) between users for transactions.</p>

  <h3>b. Images and Camera Access</h3>
  <p>The App requests access to your device’s camera and photo gallery to allow you to upload pictures of cars or parts. We do not store or access any images unless you choose to upload them.</p>

  <h3>c. Usage Data (Optional)</h3>
  <p>We may collect anonymous data like app usage statistics and crash reports to help us improve the App.</p>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To connect users via WhatsApp or direct communication.</li>
    <li>To display vehicle and auto-part listings with uploaded images.</li>
    <li>To provide customer support and app functionality.</li>
    <li>To improve the App’s performance and user experience.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
  <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or trade your personal information. We only share data:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>With other users (e.g., phone numbers for communication).</li>
    <li>With trusted third parties who support app functionality.</li>
    <li>When required by law.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>We retain your data only as long as necessary to provide our services, or as required by law.</p>

  <h2>5. Security</h2>
  <p>We use reasonable measures to protect your data, but no method of transmission is 100% secure.</p>

  <h2>6. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>You may update or delete your personal info at any time.</li>
    <li>You may revoke camera or media access through device settings.</li>
    <li>Contact us for any privacy-related questions.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>This app is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>

  <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes will be posted here. Continued use of the App means you accept the new terms.</p>

  <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions about this policy, please contact us:</p>
